WEBVTT

00:07.025 --> 00:08.774
DANNY:
I gotta take a leak.

00:08.776 --> 00:10.693
BAEZ: How many times
do I have to tell you?

00:10.695 --> 00:12.528
Caffeine is a diuretic.

00:12.530 --> 00:13.863
A what?

00:13.865 --> 00:15.831
Just switch to decaf.

00:15.833 --> 00:18.417
What fun would
that be?

00:18.419 --> 00:20.202
About as much fun as waiting
around on this lowlife.

00:20.204 --> 00:21.337
Where the
hell is he?

00:21.339 --> 00:23.122
Think I like waiting
on a junkie dirtbag

00:23.124 --> 00:24.540
any more than you do?
(sighs)

00:24.542 --> 00:25.958
Well, you won't have
to wait much longer.

00:25.960 --> 00:27.009
Tour's almost over.

00:27.011 --> 00:28.928
He's your CI.

00:28.930 --> 00:30.429
(car door opening)

00:32.934 --> 00:34.050
You know, you're
gonna buy it,

00:34.052 --> 00:35.351
you ever pull a stunt
like that again.

00:35.353 --> 00:36.969
Oh, you think I like sneaking
around like this?

00:36.971 --> 00:38.721
I can't be seen
talking to you two.

00:38.723 --> 00:39.889
Well, start talking, then.

00:39.891 --> 00:41.057
Money first.

00:41.059 --> 00:43.609
What... I think
you're high already.

00:44.729 --> 00:46.062
Talk first.

00:46.064 --> 00:47.730
Who's the new fence buying up
all the swag

00:47.732 --> 00:48.898
in the
neighborhood?

00:48.900 --> 00:49.982
See, that's-that's
big information

00:49.984 --> 00:51.067
and you know it.

00:51.069 --> 00:52.401
I want $40 and
I want it up front.

00:52.403 --> 00:53.819
DANNY:
You didn't get it, did you?

00:53.821 --> 00:55.204
You didn't get a name,
you didn't get anything.

00:55.206 --> 00:56.372
I'm getting it,
all right?

00:56.374 --> 00:58.707
It's... and I got
a really good lead.

00:58.709 --> 01:00.576
I just... I just need
to get my fix first.

01:00.578 --> 01:01.578
BAEZ:
No info,

01:01.579 --> 01:03.295
no dough.

01:06.084 --> 01:08.584
Hey!

01:08.586 --> 01:10.136
Come here.
Ah, ah, ah, ah.

01:10.138 --> 01:11.670
Come here, come here.

01:11.672 --> 01:13.139
Give me the money.

01:13.141 --> 01:15.091
Hey. Listen.

01:15.093 --> 01:16.559
You ever pull a stunt
like that again,

01:16.561 --> 01:18.594
you're going in the river,
you got it?

01:18.596 --> 01:20.012
Get out of here.

01:20.014 --> 01:21.514
Come on. Go.

01:22.984 --> 01:25.101
Go on.

01:25.103 --> 01:27.069
JANKO:
Oh....

01:27.071 --> 01:30.055
It should be illegal,
what you're doing right now.

01:30.057 --> 01:31.690
What?
Sullying the reputation

01:31.692 --> 01:33.893
of this beautiful girl.
(man singing indistinctly)

01:33.895 --> 01:35.327
She'll get over it.

01:35.329 --> 01:37.113
I'll get over it.

01:37.115 --> 01:38.864
♪ You were lost ♪

01:38.866 --> 01:41.750
♪ And gone forever ♪

01:41.752 --> 01:44.320
♪ Oh, my darling ♪

01:44.322 --> 01:46.255
♪ Charlene. ♪
(Janko chortles)

01:46.257 --> 01:47.706
Check out this
Romeo over here.

01:47.708 --> 01:50.176
Why won't you look at me?
Charlene,

01:50.178 --> 01:52.912
the least you could do
is-is look at me.

01:52.914 --> 01:54.713
Charlene!

01:56.050 --> 01:58.150
Charlene!
Whoa, hey. Hey.

01:58.920 --> 02:00.803
JAMIE:
Calm down. Hey.

02:00.805 --> 02:02.938
Hey!
Oh. Nope.

02:03.641 --> 02:05.591
JAMIE:
Hands behind your back.

02:05.593 --> 02:07.092
Give me your hands.

02:07.094 --> 02:09.027
Oh, man, you smell.

02:15.453 --> 02:16.785
What are we doing here?

02:16.787 --> 02:17.903
Ah, gettin'
some coffee.

02:17.905 --> 02:19.155
We're almost end of tour.

02:19.157 --> 02:20.372
Get one back
at the squad.

02:20.374 --> 02:21.574
It'll take two
minutes, partner.

02:21.576 --> 02:22.875
You're annoying,
you know that?

02:22.877 --> 02:23.909
I've been told.

02:23.911 --> 02:26.162
Two black.
Nah, I don't want one.

02:26.164 --> 02:27.413
Suit yourself.

02:27.415 --> 02:28.664
It's free.

02:28.666 --> 02:30.833
Thanks.

02:33.171 --> 02:35.154
I appreciate that.

02:35.156 --> 02:37.173
Psst.

02:42.346 --> 02:43.395
Hey. Hey!

02:43.397 --> 02:44.847
(grunting)

02:45.516 --> 02:46.599
(Baez screams)

02:46.601 --> 02:49.134
(groaning)

02:49.136 --> 02:50.569
(grunts)

02:52.240 --> 02:53.272
You okay?

02:53.274 --> 02:54.473
Yeah, yeah,
I'm right behind you.

02:54.475 --> 02:55.858
Gun!

03:01.749 --> 03:03.949
(panting)

03:04.952 --> 03:06.418
DANNY:
Hey!

03:07.838 --> 03:09.872
Stop! Police!

03:09.874 --> 03:11.457
Hey!

03:11.459 --> 03:12.958
Stop! Police!

03:20.935 --> 03:23.552
(grunts)

03:25.640 --> 03:27.389
Police!

03:28.209 --> 03:30.025
Hey!

03:30.645 --> 03:32.728
Move!
(woman yells)

03:37.118 --> 03:39.735
5-4 detectives requesting
a 10-13,

03:39.737 --> 03:41.403
122 Ditmars.

03:43.000 --> 03:49.074
Advertise your product or brand here
contact www.OpenSubtitles.org today

03:50.548 --> 03:51.714
Hold it!

03:54.335 --> 03:55.501
(panting)

03:55.503 --> 03:57.253
Let me see your hands.

03:57.255 --> 03:59.071
Wait, wait,
don't shoot!

03:59.073 --> 04:00.172
Shut your mouth.

04:00.174 --> 04:01.590
Hey. Back inside

04:01.592 --> 04:03.425
the apartment.

04:03.427 --> 04:04.810
(door closes)

04:04.812 --> 04:06.312
Turn around, put your
hands against the wall,

04:06.314 --> 04:08.230
or I promise I'll throw you
out that window.

04:09.567 --> 04:10.766
Hey!

04:10.768 --> 04:13.185
(screams)

04:13.187 --> 04:15.571
(grunts)

04:15.573 --> 04:16.772
(man screaming)

04:16.774 --> 04:18.072
(screaming, sobbing)

04:18.075 --> 04:19.658
My leg!
Call an ambulance!

04:19.660 --> 04:21.110
(groans)

04:21.112 --> 04:22.661
(groans)
Look at that.

04:22.663 --> 04:24.496
That cop--
he pushed me out the window!

04:24.498 --> 04:25.731
Hey, just calm down.
You did...

04:25.733 --> 04:26.999
Just stop moving!

04:27.001 --> 04:28.500
(angry murmuring)

04:28.502 --> 04:29.668
MAN: Police brutality!

04:29.670 --> 04:31.503
Police brutality!

04:31.505 --> 04:32.671
Calm down.

04:32.673 --> 04:34.406
Yo! What the hell, lady?!

04:34.408 --> 04:35.708
Okay, everybody back!

04:35.710 --> 04:37.126
(shouting indistinctly)

04:37.128 --> 04:39.044
Stay back.

04:39.046 --> 04:40.512
Stay back!

04:40.514 --> 04:43.299
MAN:
Police brutality!

04:43.353 --> 04:47.353
<font color=#00FF00>♪ Blue Bloods 5x04 ♪</font>
<font color=#00FFFF>Excessive Force</font>
